1
00:00:21,920 --> 00:00:23,040
I'm an orphan.

2
00:00:24,600 --> 00:00:26,200
When I was very young,

3
00:00:26,200 --> 00:00:28,120
my parents died in a car crash.

4
00:00:28,920 --> 00:00:30,360
Just to have food to eat,

5
00:00:31,280 --> 00:00:32,360
when I was 17,

6
00:00:32,360 --> 00:00:33,680
I got involved with Wang Dahai

7
00:00:34,240 --> 00:00:35,360
and became his mistress.

8
00:00:39,479 --> 00:00:40,439
Your feet...

9
00:00:41,520 --> 00:00:42,680
weren't like that naturally, were they?

10
00:00:42,799 --> 00:00:44,520
Wang Dahai did this to you.

11
00:00:47,520 --> 00:00:48,959
He said a woman's feet

12
00:00:49,400 --> 00:00:51,000
have to be small to be beautiful.

13
00:00:52,119 --> 00:00:53,720
The practice of foot-binding

14
00:00:54,159 --> 00:00:56,520
should be passed down through generations.

15
00:01:00,400 --> 00:01:01,200
Good girl.

16
00:01:01,840 --> 00:01:03,119
So beautiful.

17
00:01:04,040 --> 00:01:06,080
I'll make you even more beautiful.

18
00:01:14,239 --> 00:01:16,680
Such delicate beauty is hard to describe,

19
00:01:16,959 --> 00:01:20,080
it must be admired in the palm of a hand.

20
00:01:22,239 --> 00:01:25,760
The ancients truly didn't deceive me.

21
00:01:29,400 --> 00:01:30,199
Exquisite.

22
00:01:30,959 --> 00:01:33,080
Truly exquisite.

23
00:01:35,040 --> 00:01:37,040
Though we bound them a bit late,

24
00:01:37,040 --> 00:01:40,160
the results are still quite excellent.

25
00:01:40,639 --> 00:01:42,000
Tonight,

26
00:01:42,959 --> 00:01:44,680
I'll indulge in some refinement too.

27
00:01:57,680 --> 00:01:59,199
Did you know he was hurting you?

28
00:02:04,760 --> 00:02:05,559
Why didn't you run?

29
00:02:07,120 --> 00:02:08,360
I was too young then.

30
00:02:09,360 --> 00:02:10,440
I didn't understand anything.

31
00:02:11,800 --> 00:02:13,440
I thought that by feeding me

32
00:02:14,080 --> 00:02:14,919
and clothing me,

33
00:02:15,960 --> 00:02:17,360
he was treating me well,

34
00:02:17,679 --> 00:02:18,559
and that he loved me.

35
00:02:20,119 --> 00:02:22,080
By the time I finally realized the truth,

36
00:02:22,960 --> 00:02:24,240
it was already too late.

37
00:02:25,240 --> 00:02:26,119
My feet were ruined.

38
00:02:26,960 --> 00:02:27,839
I couldn't run.

39
00:02:31,360 --> 00:02:32,720
Since your legs and feet are impaired,

40
00:02:33,759 --> 00:02:35,240
how did you kidnap Wang Dongdong?

41
00:02:36,479 --> 00:02:37,279
That wasn't hard.

42
00:02:39,320 --> 00:02:40,600
That little jerk

43
00:02:41,839 --> 00:02:44,160
has the same kink as his father.

44
00:03:06,679 --> 00:03:07,399
Your feet...

45
00:03:09,240 --> 00:03:10,320
have always been in pain, haven't they?

46
00:03:13,119 --> 00:03:13,839
They hurt.

47
00:03:15,559 --> 00:03:16,240
A lot.

48
00:03:18,360 --> 00:03:19,479
It really hurts.

49
00:03:22,240 --> 00:03:24,240
Every minute after that,

50
00:03:25,360 --> 00:03:26,199
every second,

51
00:03:27,000 --> 00:03:28,600
every step I took,

52
00:03:31,320 --> 00:03:32,839
every day I lived,

53
00:03:34,520 --> 00:03:36,520
the pain made me want to die.

54
00:03:39,199 --> 00:03:40,600
But I couldn't die.

55
00:03:41,520 --> 00:03:42,000
Darn it,

56
00:03:42,000 --> 00:03:43,440
those jerks are the ones who should die,

57
00:03:44,440 --> 00:03:46,720
those jerks who treat women like toys.

58
00:03:53,600 --> 00:03:55,039
But I failed.

59
00:03:55,960 --> 00:03:56,759
I was too weak.

60
00:04:01,720 --> 00:04:02,360
No.

61
00:04:02,919 --> 00:04:03,679
I'm still here.

62
00:04:07,600 --> 00:04:08,440
I'm here too.

63
00:04:46,279 --> 00:04:47,160
Don't sleep yet.

64
00:04:47,440 --> 00:04:48,359
Change your clothes,

65
00:04:48,440 --> 00:04:49,480
wash up, then sleep.

66
00:04:49,519 --> 00:04:51,239
I'm not sleeping, I'm just resting my eyes.

67
00:04:53,959 --> 00:04:55,119
Get up.

68
00:04:55,440 --> 00:04:57,200
Five minutes.

69
00:05:04,119 --> 00:05:04,559
Pajamas.

70
00:05:05,959 --> 00:05:07,239
Just five minutes.

71
00:05:07,239 --> 00:05:08,640
Then I'll get up and shower.

72
00:05:21,640 --> 00:05:22,480
Suit yourself.

73
00:05:50,799 --> 00:05:52,519
Happy birthday, Lin Shen.

74
00:05:52,959 --> 00:05:54,839
I really am your best friend.

75
00:05:55,200 --> 00:05:57,799
This watch cost me a month's salary.

76
00:05:58,079 --> 00:05:59,679
When my birthday comes around,

77
00:05:59,679 --> 00:06:02,160
don't you dare forget to get me a gift.

78
00:06:02,239 --> 00:06:03,000
And...

79
00:06:03,279 --> 00:06:04,279
I want an expensive one.

80
00:06:36,119 --> 00:06:37,160
The person in this photo...

81
00:06:37,760 --> 00:06:38,839
who is it, exactly?

82
00:06:43,760 --> 00:06:45,519
How much more are you hiding from me?

83
00:06:50,640 --> 00:06:51,239
Come with me.

84
00:07:50,920 --> 00:07:51,600
Lin Shen.

85
00:09:03,239 --> 00:09:03,799
Uncle...

86
00:09:04,760 --> 00:09:05,679
I'm here to see you.

87
00:09:16,599 --> 00:09:17,559
Have you been well lately?

88
00:09:19,640 --> 00:09:20,880
Yesterday was my birthday.

89
00:09:22,200 --> 00:09:23,400
Actually, after you left,

90
00:09:25,919 --> 00:09:27,119
I never celebrated it again.

91
00:09:29,719 --> 00:09:31,359
Because every year I remember

92
00:09:33,400 --> 00:09:34,159
back then...

93
00:09:35,200 --> 00:09:36,559
you were hurrying back for my birthday

94
00:09:36,559 --> 00:09:37,599
when you passed away.

95
00:09:38,159 --> 00:09:39,840
So I never celebrated it again after that.

96
00:09:48,760 --> 00:09:49,799
But I didn't expect that

97
00:09:51,400 --> 00:09:51,960
this year,

98
00:09:53,159 --> 00:09:53,679
that little dummy

99
00:09:53,679 --> 00:09:55,359
would actually get me a birthday gift.

100
00:09:59,239 --> 00:10:00,159
Her name is Lu Yi.

101
00:10:01,440 --> 00:10:02,559
She's my

102
00:10:04,280 --> 00:10:05,080
good friend.

103
00:10:08,799 --> 00:10:10,479
But she's also Lawyer Lu Yong's daughter.

104
00:10:12,239 --> 00:10:14,119
And she's been investigating this case too.

105
00:10:18,080 --> 00:10:19,000
I'm scared.

106
00:10:20,520 --> 00:10:22,280
I know your death back then wasn't an accident.

107
00:10:23,520 --> 00:10:25,239
So I'm afraid she'll also...

108
00:10:31,159 --> 00:10:32,880
It's enough for me to walk this road alone.

109
00:10:39,359 --> 00:10:40,039
Uncle...

110
00:10:41,239 --> 00:10:42,039
Don't worry.

111
00:10:42,320 --> 00:10:43,119
With me here,

112
00:10:44,159 --> 00:10:45,440
I will...

113
00:10:45,880 --> 00:10:46,679
one by one,

114
00:10:47,520 --> 00:10:49,400
send those scumbags to prison.

115
00:10:50,960 --> 00:10:51,719
I will get you...

116
00:10:52,640 --> 00:10:54,599
and all those innocent people justice.

117
00:10:59,320 --> 00:11:00,000
I'll be going now.

118
00:11:33,000 --> 00:11:33,599
Hello?

119
00:11:34,159 --> 00:11:34,919
Lu Yi.

120
00:11:35,280 --> 00:11:36,239
Something happened to your dad.

121
00:11:38,080 --> 00:11:39,280
Mom, what did you say?

122
00:11:39,599 --> 00:11:40,760
Something happened to your dad.

123
00:11:40,880 --> 00:11:42,080
He's at the hospital right now.

124
00:11:45,200 --> 00:11:45,919
Lin Shen.

125
00:11:47,159 --> 00:11:48,520
You really have a lot of secrets.

126
00:12:00,880 --> 00:12:01,599
Then I'll just say it.

127
00:12:04,239 --> 00:12:05,039
First,

128
00:12:05,159 --> 00:12:06,440
on behalf of Boss Wang,

129
00:12:06,559 --> 00:12:08,760
I'd like to express to you officers

130
00:12:08,840 --> 00:12:10,000
our sincere thanks.

131
00:12:11,719 --> 00:12:13,520
Thank you, officers,

132
00:12:13,679 --> 00:12:15,599
for your bravery and fearlessness,

133
00:12:15,880 --> 00:12:17,039
for serving the people wholeheartedly,

134
00:12:17,359 --> 00:12:18,479
and for solving the case so quickly.

135
00:12:18,880 --> 00:12:19,719
To you,

136
00:12:19,799 --> 00:12:20,559
we express our gratitude.

137
00:12:23,200 --> 00:12:23,840
Boss Wang,

138
00:12:25,239 --> 00:12:26,320
you're really too polite.

139
00:12:26,320 --> 00:12:28,119
Knowing how hard we work to catch suspects,

140
00:12:28,119 --> 00:12:29,840
so you delivered yourself right to our door.

141
00:12:32,280 --> 00:12:33,280
Look carefully.

142
00:12:35,559 --> 00:12:36,359
Wang Dahai.

143
00:12:37,159 --> 00:12:37,960
You're suspected of

144
00:12:37,960 --> 00:12:38,640
intentional assault,

145
00:12:38,640 --> 00:12:39,440
tax evasion,

146
00:12:39,440 --> 00:12:40,239
and indecent assault.

147
00:12:40,719 --> 00:12:41,799
For the above charges,

148
00:12:41,799 --> 00:12:42,799
the evidence is conclusive.

149
00:12:42,880 --> 00:12:44,880
You are hereby under arrest.

150
00:12:56,799 --> 00:12:58,280
What happened to Lu Yi's father

151
00:12:58,280 --> 00:13:00,159
cast a huge shadow over her.

152
00:13:00,520 --> 00:13:02,039
But after she joined your team,

153
00:13:02,039 --> 00:13:03,679
her condition has improved a lot.

154
00:13:05,760 --> 00:13:06,799
That's a good thing.

155
00:13:09,359 --> 00:13:09,960
Doctor Yuan,

156
00:13:10,400 --> 00:13:11,080
don't worry.

157
00:13:11,599 --> 00:13:13,239
I'll take good care of my team.
